      "content": "hey so i have a question about my insulin. i normally take my basal dose in the evening but i barely ate anything for dinner tonight, like just a tiny bit of salad. would it be okay if i just skipped my dose tonight to be safe so my sugar doesnt drop too low while i sleep?",
